-- Ebro Sees Substantial Boost to 2012 Profit, CEO Tells Expansion
-- B y   B e n   S i l l s
-- 2011-12-31T11:44:07Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-31/ebro-sees-substantial-boost-to-2012-profit-ceo-tells-expansion.html
Ebro Foods SA (EBRO)  will see profit
improve “substantially” next year as the price of wheat and
rice drops, Chairman Antonio Hernandez Callejas told  Expansion .  The company may pay an extraordinary dividend, he told the
newspaper in an interview. Ebro’s sales are set to rise 9.4
percent to 1.8 billion euros ($2.3 billion) in 2011, the
newspaper added.  To contact the reporter on this story:
